{"tid":1341361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗無政府狀態 勇武隨意發揮","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:32.000Z","uid":72354,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5d8ca736a54d8d672ece0800c3f03f77c9ffb8","tid":1341361,"uid":72354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"相信大家都明白<br />\n無論點樣同政府或警犬對立都好<br />\n所做到既野都係有限<br />\n因為大家都係奉公守法既市民<br />\n加上傳媒鏡頭影住哂<br />\n有D野唔會去到太盡<br />\n但係今次元朗單野就唔同講法<br />\n場交就佢地聊起先<br />\n加上明顯黑警又偏幫佢地<br />\n令到元朗已經成為無執法者既地方<br />\n既然元朗咁樣衝出黎擋刀<br />\n大家就成全佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左光復之外<br />\n打遊擊都係唔錯既選擇<br />\n唔熟元朗地形既可以先入去踩線先<br />\n等熟左地形之後再自由發揮各種活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如參觀祠堂,山墳<br />\n睇下周圍D靚車有無比人整花整損<br />\n幫手留意下D丁屋既玻璃結構穩唔穩固<br />\n食肆環境夠唔夠衛生等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保護元朗, 人人有責!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下開放留言各種創意活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19dc1e69e161ef1c1f43d73088597de9ad7e4621","tid":1341361,"uid":72354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c57d076823bc08f88a4ab78d99fa95bed81ad8","tid":1341361,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br /